    9 A-C Grades including English, Maths, Science, ICT

    <h3>Interests:</h3>

    <p>Outside of the web I am a keen cyclist, riding both on and off road, and fall of more than I would care to admit. I attend lots of gigs and festivals, and in a past life ran a local music blog, interviewing and reviewing local bands for my website / local press. I’m also a amateur photographer, preferring to shoot on film rather than digital.</p>

